Each finding includes runnable example test code following existing patterns (`TestClient` + `dependency_overrides` for backend, RTL + `vi.mock` for frontend). The dialog tests that exist are high-quality (behavior-focused, DAMP, accessible queries) — the gap is breadth, not depth.
